description:
created in the class AHST 651 - Regional Modernism: The New Orleans Archives,  Tulane School of Architecture, Spring 2008, Francine J. Stock Instructor. describing architecture built in New Orleans c. 1925-1975
Primary sources are the New Orleans Public Libary's Index to Building Plans online and the Southeastern Architectual Archives finding aids.
